      - info
      - warning
      - error

channel.docs: Chat channel for testing custom method names

chat.yml.rawContents:
channel:
  path: /v1/ws/chat
  url: production
  auth: false
  docs: Chat channel for testing custom method names
  messages:
    serverNotification:
      origin: server
      body: root.ServerNotificationPayload
      method-name: onNotification
    userMessage:
      origin: client
      body: root.UserMessagePayload
  examples:
    - messages: []
imports:
  root: __package__.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
environments:
  production: wss://api.example.com
default-environment: production
default-url: Base
